data.description: Fantastic Home with a low HOA. 4 bedroom, 2 bath home w/over 1,600 ht. sq. ft. Formal living room. Family room and dining room are open to the Kitchen. Kitchen offers stainless steel appliances, granite counter tops, solid wood cabinets, breakfast bar and island. Master bath offer garden tub with separate shower. Tile throughout the home. Inside utility room. Screened porche with a huge patio, fenced in yard and a lot of fruit trees . 2 car garage. Near to schools, shopping and much more. Must see it !!!  Make your appointment today.
